passive.name: Raging Waves
passive.description: Increases the wearer's CRIT Rate by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color>. After a CRIT Hit, there is a <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> fixed chance to dispel 1 buff on the target enemy. This effect can only trigger 1 time per attack.
